reviewText: Great movies! You get 3 movies on this dvd. Its great, all 3 cartoon movies are good. Kids will enjoy them! The 1st movie: Planet 51- its about a human that goes to an alien planet (the aliens think the human is the "alien"). The 2nd movie: Pirates! Band of misfits- its about a pirate that wants to win the best pirate award. The 3rd movie: Surf's Up- its about a peguin who wants to become the best surfer.
